{"tid":1132112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：中國青年要「聽黨話、跟黨走」","createTime":"2019-04-30T05:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T15:50:27.000Z","uid":22422,"like":21,"dislike":308,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"9c58a74400bbb057daf915aa6710b6d47913150c","tid":1132112,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"習近平：中國青年要「聽黨話、跟黨走」<br />\n2019-04-30 HKT 11:35<br />\n<br />\n \t<br />\n本台北京新聞中心記者李大煒報道<br />\n國家主席習近平於紀念五四運動100周年活動上表示，愛國是每個中國人的責任和本分，亦是新時代中國青年立身之本，成材之基。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又引用孫中山的說話，指出背叛國家和欺騙國家的人，丟臉和沒有立足之地。習近平又說，愛國主義本質，就是愛黨、愛國、愛社會主義，以及高度統一。<br />\n<br />\n習近平說，中國青年要「聽黨話、跟黨走」，不斷奉獻祖國和人民，需要迎難而上的擔當精神，逃避責任的思想要不得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455277-20190430.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455277-20190430.htm&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1RTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6c69efc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455277-20190430.htm&h=08412f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455277-20190430.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0a31edd7ae2ae8ff6a5372bc519d9e16272fa90c","tid":1132112,"uid":211645,"like":381,"dislike":2,"score":379,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c3e080f76f08fb38726b7b673a0961f9552d204","tid":1132112,"uid":3241,"like":167,"dislike":2,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"食屎啦小學雞維尼"},{"pid":"a8a572845e77952299619f5e8a127a2ead33bd1d","tid":1132112,"uid":14103,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"回血劍！"},{"pid":"ac4a9a168283039085ceda0aa4f6cbef1afffef7","tid":1132112,"uid":22422,"like":239,"dislike":0,"score":239,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vpuYoE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F