da0aa4f6cbef1afffef7","tid":1132112,"uid":22422,"like":239,"dislike":0,"score":239,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vpuYoE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vpuYoE.gif&h=989e0d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽黨話 跟黨走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"跟黨走=移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc9f9576a9a5068716b1ee025a3762a773c16f0","tid":1132112,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bdb7786ca6089bbb0c286afbca53b80099c6e2c","tid":1132112,"uid":137789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習近平：中國青年要「聽黨話、跟黨走」<br />\n2019-04-30 HKT 11:35<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n本台北京新聞中心記者李大煒報道<br />\n國家主席習近平於紀念五四運動100周年活動上表示，愛國是每個中國人的責任和本分，亦是新時代中國青年立身之本，成材之基。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又引用孫中山的說話，指出背叛國家和欺騙國家的人，丟臉和沒有立足之地。習近平又說，愛國主義本質，就是愛黨、愛國、愛社會主義，以及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高度統一</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n習近平說，中國青年要「聽黨話、跟黨走」，不斷奉獻祖國和人民，需要迎難而上的擔當精神，逃避責任的思想要不得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455277-20190430.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455277-20190430.htm&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1RTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6c69efc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455277-20190430.htm&h=08412f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455277-20190430.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">高度自治</span>不是自治，<span style=\"color: red;\">高度統一</span>一定不是統一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"隻小學維尼熊敢粒聲唔出就郁台灣嘅話<br />\n我就掛佢幅相喺間房<br />\n日日跪一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\"